The paper is focused on security metrics, which is a subfield of computer security (cs.CR). It also discusses the importance of measuring defenses and threats, which are relevant to software engineering (cs.SE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions cyber attacks, which falls under the category of cyber security (cs.CY) and the outcomes of cyber attack-defense interactions, which is related to systems and information science (cs.SI).
